  "shortDescription": "A dynamic stretch to increase mobility in the hips by performing circular leg movements.",
  "instructions": "Stand upright and place your hands on your hips. Lift one knee and move your leg in a controlled circular motion from the hip joint, reversing direction as needed; repeat with the other leg.",
  "steps": [
    "Stand tall with feet shoulder-width apart, hands on hips.",
    "Lift one knee up in front of you.",
    "Move your knee and thigh in a circular motion outward.",
    "Reverse and perform circles inward after the set.",
    "Switch legs and repeat."
  ],
